n mind cops do this all the time and their word is better than Maybe though they don't guess how fast bikes are going all the Besides this guy didn't speak English very well and ended up absolutely confounding the judge the cop and everyone else in the room who'd been recently criminalized by some twit with a gun and a OK I'm better Maybe he'd have won had his presentation been more Maybe He did get